node.text:
Rise, Tarnished.

#ELDENRING comes to PlayStation, Xbox, and PC Digital January 21, 2022.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on June 23, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, outdoors and text that says 'ELDEN RING'.

node.text:
A lord clings to his ruined Legacy; the ruler of a husk wrung dry by war.

#ELDENRING

node.text:
Foul deeds brought the Shattering to these lands. Fouler deeds yet may still be afoot. ​
​
#ELDENRING

node.text:
The Lands Between are vast, but a Tarnished need not walk their path alone. ​
​
#ELDENRING

node.text:
Like the Erdtree itself, a Tarnished's path reaches up to the branches of the heavens and twists down into the roots of the earth. ​
​
#ELDENRING

node.text:
The Lands Between basked in the pure light of the Greater Will before the Shattering. 

Slivers of its blessing yet remain in hidden pockets where lost graces wait to be found. #ELDENRING

node.text:
Rise, Tarnished.

#ELDENRING comes to PlayStation, Xbox, and PC Digital January 21, 2022.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on September 26, 2019.

node.text: “The importance we place on the joy the player experiences through overcoming challenges will be the same as it is in our other titles. I believe it will prove to be a very satisfying experience.” - Hidetaka Miyazaki #ELDENRING

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on September 18, 2019. May be an image of text that says 'THE START OF THIS COLLABORATION caME FROM THE FACT THATI MYSELF AM A HUGE FAN OF MR. MARTIN' S WORK. HIDETAKA MIYAZAKI ELDENRING ELDEN RING'.

node.text: “The start of this collaboration came from the fact that I myself am a huge fan of Mr. Martin’s work.” - Hidetaka Miyazaki #ELDENRING

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on September 08, 2019.

node.text: “This #ELDENRING has been shattered. The significance of this will be one of the important themes of the game.” - Hidetaka Miyazaki

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on September 03, 2019.

Photo by ELDEN RING on August 30, 2019. May be an image of text that says 'THIS TITLE THIITILL WILL INCLUDE A WIDE VARIETY OF WEAPONS MAGIC, AND WAYS TO ENGAGE ENEMIES. HIDETAKA YAZAKI ELDENRING ELDEN RING'.

node.text:
“This title will include a wide variety of weapons, magic, and ways to engage enemies.” - Hidetaka Miyazaki
#ELDENRING

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ELDEN RING on August 27, 2019.

node.text:
“Mr. Martin and I had many free and creative conversations regarding the game.” - Hidetaka Miyazaki
#ELDENRING
